related_to.description: A relationship that exists between two entities

affects.description: Indicates that one entity affects another

rules.description: Every Material has at least one Property
If a Method modifies a Property and a Material has that Property, then the Method can be used on the Material
If a Material has certain Property values, it can be classified as a specific type
rules.rule: Material(?m) && has_property(?m, ?p) && Property(?p) && has_value(?p, ?v) && greaterThan(?v, threshold) -> MaterialType(?m)
